Caption Breanna Stewart, UConn, First Team, Player Of The Year MICHAEL McANDREWS / Hartford Courant Breanna Stewart shoots jumpers during warm-ups before playing South Florida. The University of Connecticut Huskies play the University of South Florida Bulls in the final game of the regular women's basketball season.

UConn won, 89-33.

(Cloe Poisson / Hartford Courant) See more galleries The American Athletic Conference announced its preseason women's basketball first and second teams on Monday, Oct. 26.
